### 层级依赖规则

| 层级 | 依赖关系 |
|------|----------|
| World | 无依赖 |
| Host | 依赖 World |
| Host Extension | 依赖 Host, World |
| moba.runtime | 依赖 Host, World, Host Extension |
| Coordinator | 依赖 Host, World |
| Game | 依赖所有层 |

