### 2.6 Builder 模式

Host 包提供了 `IWorldHostBuilder` 用于灵活组装组件：

```csharp
// 最小配置
var host = WorldHostBuilder.Create()
    .SetWorldFactory(new DefaultWorldFactory())
    .Build();

// 帧同步服务器配置
var host = WorldHostBuilder.Create()
    .SetWorldFactory(new DefaultWorldFactory(blueprintRegistry))
    .SetTimeDriver(new FixedStepTimeDriver { FrameRate = 30 })
    .SetInputDriver(new LocalInputDriver())
    .SetSnapshotProvider(new SimpleSnapshotProvider(snapshotProvider))
    .AddModule(new FrameSyncDriverModule())
    .Build();
```

