## 三、Coordinator 包 (com.abilitykit.coordinator)

### 3.1 核心定位

Coordinator 包是**通用战斗会话协调框架**，封装了帧同步/状态同步的复杂性，让接入方只需实现少量接口即可接入不同的战斗逻辑世界。

### 3.2 核心组件

| 组件 | 文件 | 职责 |
|------|------|------|
| `SessionCoordinator` | `Runtime/Core/SessionCoordinator.cs` | 会话生命周期管理 |
| `ISessionCoordinator` | `Runtime/Core/ISessionCoordinator.cs` | 会话协调器接口 |
| `ISessionCoordinatorHost` | `Runtime/Core/ISessionCoordinatorHost.cs` | 宿主接口 |
| `IBattleDriverHost` | `Runtime/Core/IBattleDriverHost.cs` | 战斗驱动宿主 |
| `ISyncAdapter` | `Runtime/Adapters/ISyncAdapter.cs` | 同步策略接口 |
| `SessionHooks` | `Runtime/Core/SessionHooks.cs` | 会话生命周期事件钩子 |
| `SessionConfig` | `Runtime/Core/SessionConfig.cs` | 会话配置 |
| `SessionState` | `Runtime/Core/SessionEnums.cs` | 会话状态枚举 |

### 3.3 SessionCoordinator 职责划分

```csharp
public sealed class SessionCoordinator : ISessionCoordinator
{
    // State
    private SessionConfig _config;
    private ISessionCoordinatorHost _host;
    private SessionState _state = SessionState.Idle;

    // World
    private IWorldHost _worldHost;
    private IWorld _world;
    private IWorldResolver _worldResolver;

    // Sync
    private ISyncAdapter _syncAdapter;
    private IBattleDriverHost _driverHost;
    private Timeline.IViewTimeline _viewTimeline;

    // View
    private IViewEventSink _viewEventSink;

    // SubFeatures
    private readonly List<SubFeatures.ISessionSubFeature> _subFeatures = new List<SubFeatures.ISessionSubFeature>();

    // Hooks
    private readonly SessionHooks _hooks = new SessionHooks();
}
```

**职责说明**：
- **World 管理**：创建、销毁世界，获取服务
- **Sync 管理**：创建 SyncAdapter，处理输入提交
- **View 桥接**：通知视图事件
- **SubFeature 扩展**：生命周期管理
- **Hooks 事件**：发布生命周期事件

### 3.4 SubFeature 扩展机制

```csharp
public interface ISessionSubFeature
{
    string Name { get; }
    int Priority { get; }
    void OnAttach(ISessionHost host);
    void OnDetach();
    void OnTick(float deltaTime);
}
```

**内置 SubFeature**：

| SubFeature | 优先级 | 职责 |
|------------|--------|------|
| `SessionEventsSubFeature` | 1000 | 会话生命周期事件管理 |
| `SessionTickLoopSubFeature` | 500 | 帧循环控制 |
| `SessionSnapshotRoutingSubFeature` | 300 | 快照路由和分发 |

### 3.5 SyncAdapter 策略模式

```csharp
public static class SyncAdapterFactory
{
    public static ISyncAdapter Create(IWorld world, in SessionConfig config)
    {
        return config.SyncMode switch
        {
            Core.SyncMode.Lockstep => CreateLocalSyncAdapter(world, config),
            Core.SyncMode.SnapshotAuthority => CreateRemoteSyncAdapter(world, config),
            Core.SyncMode.StateSync => CreateRemoteSyncAdapter(world, config),
            Core.SyncMode.Hybrid => CreateHybridSyncAdapter(world, config),
            _ => CreateLocalSyncAdapter(world, config)
        };
    }
}
```

| 同步模式 | 适配器 | 适用场景 |
|----------|--------|----------|
| `Lockstep` | `LocalSyncAdapter` | 单机、局域网 |
| `StateSync` | `RemoteSyncAdapter` | 网络游戏，服务器权威 |
| `Hybrid` | `HybridSyncAdapter` | 网络游戏 + 客户端预测 |

